{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9028bb2cc0","title":"毛泽东关于庐山会议简报上应一律称同志问题给刘少奇等的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d43e5f8e76","index":0,"year":1959,"month":8,"day":3,"articleId":"9028bb2cc0"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d7baf5c033","type":"title","text":"毛泽东关于庐山会议简报上应一律称同志问题给刘少奇等的信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9028bb2cc0"},{"id":"1ab9d8a361","type":"paragraph","text":"少奇、恩来、彭真、尚昆同志，各组组长同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9028bb2cc0"},{"id":"b2018e15d9","type":"paragraph","text":"简报上对于同志的称呼不妥当，这种旧习惯应当改过来。建议：一律称某某同志。例如：主席，称毛泽东同志；总理，称周恩来同志；林总，彭总，贺总，称林彪同志，彭德怀同志，贺龙同志。其他，以此类推。如同意，请各组长在会上宣布一下。请尚昆告简报编者，一律从四日起照此改正。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9028bb2cc0"},{"id":"722fc02623","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东八月三日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9028bb2cc0"}],"page":{"id":"b18cef5539","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9028bb2cc0","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}